      "text": "A variable is something that varies (changes in value). It may not be measurable in the normal sense of the word but it must be capable of changing – up and down. For example, the quantity of food my horse eats; the amount of work he does; the condition of my horse; the amount of motivation he has; his acceptance of the bit. These are all variables. ",
